<L>__{exterior the rose theatre. evening.}
<A>__{the closure notice is nailed to the door.}
<L>__{interior de lessepses' house. viola's bedroom. night.}
<A>__{viola, in her nightdress, is reading by candlelight. she is reading her private manuscript of romeo and juliet...and rereading. next to her is a tray of covered dishes. the nurse enters and looks at her sympathetically. she lifts the tray. she realises it is heavy. she puts it down and raises the covers and sees that viola has eaten nothing. she looks at viola's tears, but there is nothing to be said.}
